<sample sampleID="LBt3_00009" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBt3_00009_F001">
<paragraph>
<sentence>　一体<quote>「宇宙人みたいな生き物」</quote><sampling type="start" />とは誰のことか？</sentence>
<sentence>　実は娘のことを話している鬼嫁なのだった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">（二十一）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">２００４年５月２９日（土）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>俺のドラクエ、知りません？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<sentence type="quasi">最近は、プレステのドラゴンクエストⅤに夢中な俺（＊´∀｀）ノ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">仕事とスロット稼動の合い間をぬって、ようやく最後のボスまで辿り着いた∩（゜∀゜∩）わっちょい</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">謎解きで詰まり、ドラクエ専用掲示板で質問したものの…、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">小学生</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「はあ？</sentence>
<sentence>　（゜Д゜）過去ログ読め！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「（；´Д｀）ノ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>そんな辛い目に遭いながら、ようやくここまで辿り着いた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>いよいよ今日は、ラストのボスを倒しに行く。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>…が、肝心のソフトがどこにも見当たらない（゜Д゜≡゜Д゜）？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>どこを探しても見当たらない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おい！</sentence>
<sentence>　ドラクエⅤのソフト知らないか？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ドラクエ？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　あぁぁぁ〜ドラクエね…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>そういいながら、嫁が冷蔵庫からモンブランを取り出してきた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「いや、モンブランじゃなくて、ドラクエを聞いてるんだが（汗）」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ドラクエでしょ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">あれなら…ブックオフが３０００円で引き取ってくれたわよ♪」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なっ（゜Д゜）…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「で、そのお金で帰りにケーキ買ってきたのよ♪」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「お前、ふざけんなよ！</sentence>
<sentence>　何で俺のゲームを勝手に売るんか！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ヽ（｀Д´；）／」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あんたが出しっぱなしにしてるからやないね！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（怒）」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「出しっぱなし…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あたしゃ、いつも言ってるわよね！</sentence>
<sentence>　直さなかったら勝手に処分するからね！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　って」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<noteBody>
<sentence type="quasi">注）直す：<quote>「片付ける」</quote>の九州弁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</noteBody>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「確かにいつも言われているが…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">でも、本当に処分することないですやん（´Д⊂グスン）</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あんたが本やゲームを片付けないのがいけないんでしょ！</sentence>
<sentence>　みせしめよ！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「（；´Д｀）ノ…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>小学生の頃、母親にいつも言われていた…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">母親</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「直さなかったら捨てるわよ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>でも、いつもちゃんと片付けてくれていた母ちゃん…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">甘えてた俺が悪かった＿｜￣｜○</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">２００４年７月６日（火）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">電話に出ないとこうなります</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<sentence>うちの嫁はとんでもないくらいの負けず嫌い。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>特に、旦那である俺に対しては異常なまでの執念を燃やすからやっかいだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>日曜日の夜…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>普段は肌身離さず持ち歩いている携帯電話だが、今日に限って忘れていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">夜になって、今日初めて携帯電話を見てみると…</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>（　゜Д゜）ポカーン…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">（つд⊂）ゴシゴシ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>（；゜д゜）…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">（つд⊂）ゴシゴシ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">＿，．＿</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>（；゜Д゜）…！？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<list>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">１２：１５…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：３２…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：４８…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">１３：０８…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：２４…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：３８…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：５５…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">１４：１２…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：２８…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：４１…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：５８…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">１５：１７…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence type="quasi">：２９…嫁の着信</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
</list>
<sentence type="quasi">以降、約２０分ごとに嫁の着信が繰り返されている（；´∀｀）…うわぁ…</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">最後の着信は２０：５６</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">これまでの８時間３０分の間に、なんと２５件の着信をつけられた（汗）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ヽ（´Д｀；≡；´Д｀）ノ　アワワ…　何か緊急事態勃発なのか？</sentence>
<sentence>　まさか、娘の身に何か起きたとでもいうのか？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>慌てて嫁に電話をしてみる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おい！</sentence>
<sentence>　何かあったのか？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「…あんたさあ、いい度胸してるわよね！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（怒）」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">カズマ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「いい度胸？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">嫁</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「私の電話を無<sampling type="end" />視するなんて、あんたも偉くなったもんよね！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（怒）」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
